Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Class JSPSourceLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp.JSPSourceLocation
  • public class JSPSourceLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a location in a JSP source file. Used for mapping compilation errors from generated Java code back to the original JSP source.
    Author:
    Chris Burdess

    • Method Summary

      java.lang.String getElementType()
      Returns the JSP element type (e.g., "scriptlet", "expression"), or null if not specified.

      Returns the column number in the JSP file (1-based), or 0 if not available.
